I te mea o te roa o te roa o te whenua, kāore ngā āhuatanga o te whenua i taea te haere, ā, ko te toroa iti te āhua matua o te whenua ki Galapagos.

I te wā e toro ana koe ki ngā rohe Arctic rānei ki te Antarctic i te wā o te hotoke ka kitea te ata polar, e ai ki tērā kāore te marama e heke mai i te rangi.
I tukuna tēnei wā he wā pai kia kitea e te Aurora borealis, nā te mea ka kauka ake te rangi i te wā o te hāora.
I te mea kei te noho iti ngā wāhi, ā, kāore i te raru i te wā o te hiko, ka taea hoki koe te whai i ngā rangi.
I āhua kē te noho mahi o Japan he kēkē ake te noho ā-ture me te āhua o te wā e whakamahia ana e ngā tāngata o Ūropi.
I kīia e ngā kaimahi he āhuatanga ture o te mahi, ā, ka kī ngā kaimahi i a rātou i ō rātou ingoa matua rānei i ō rātou ingoa mahi.
I whai wāhi te noho tahi o te whare mahi, ā, ka whakaaturia te mahi a te hunga whai wāhi, ā, kāore i te whakanui i ngā tutukitanga o ngā tāngata.
I ā rātou wā e whai ana ngā kaimahi kia whai i te tautoko a ō rātou kaiārahi mō ngā whakatau e whakatau ana, ā, kei te whai i a rātou ngā whakahau a ō rātou kaiārahi e kore e whai āwangawanga.
